      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen has undergone meticulous mechanical stewardship, including a documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement plates to ensure torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and delivered through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the precise handling characteristics of the M-division's gold standard. Finished with a professional-grade paint correction, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning purist.",
