      "description": "Offered for sale is a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman, preserved in flawless showroom condition. The Guards Red exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating applied shortly after purchase; the body is entirely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, featuring smoke-free black leather with zero bolster wear and factory-fresh carpeting. Mechanically, this vehicle is indistinguishable from new, having been exclusively serviced at authorized Porsche centers with a complete, documented maintenance log. Every feature, from the Bose Surround Sound system to the Sport Chrono package, functions perfectly. This car has been strictly garaged, never tracked, and driven only in fair weather, making it a rare find for a discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection.",
